CountofMembers_1.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.LoyRcg_LoyaltyLedger_ManualActions66.FullyQualifiedName}";q = filter q by 'IncludeInManualActions' == "True";q = filter q by {{column(LoyaltyProgramCurren_1.selection, ["NQP_Currency"]).asEquality('LoyaltyProgramCurrency_NQP_Currency')}} or ('LoyaltyProgramCurrency_QP_Currency' is not null && {{column(LoyaltyProgramCurren_2.selection, ["LoyaltyProgramCurrency_QP_Currency"]).asEquality('LoyaltyProgramCurrency_QP_Currency')}});q = filter q by 'TransactionJournal_Status' == "Processed";q_Duration = filter q by {{row(ActivityDate_2.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('ActivityDate_Year', 'ActivityDate_Month', 'ActivityDate_Day')")}};q_Duration =  group q_Duration by 'LoyaltyProgramMemberId' ;q_Duration = foreach q_Duration generate 'LoyaltyProgramMemberId' as 'LoyaltyMemberId', count() as 'count';q_CompareToDuration = filter q by {{row(ActivityDate_3.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('ActivityDate_Year', 'ActivityDate_Month', 'ActivityDate_Day')")}};q_CompareToDuration =  group q_CompareToDuration by 'LoyaltyProgramMemberId';q_CompareToDuration = foreach q_CompareToDuration generate 'LoyaltyProgramMemberId' as 'LoyaltyMemberId', count() as 'count';hist = load "${App.Datasets.LoyRcg_LoyaltyMemberTierHistory40.FullyQualifiedName}";hist_Duration= filter hist by {{row(ActivityDate_2.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year', 'CreatedDate_Month', 'CreatedDate_Day')")}};hist_Duration = group hist_Duration by 'LoyaltyMemberTier_LoyaltyMemberId';hist_Duration = foreach hist_Duration generate  'LoyaltyMemberTier_LoyaltyMemberId' as 'LoyaltyMemberId', count() as 'count';hist_CompareToDuration = filter hist by {{row(ActivityDate_3.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year', 'CreatedDate_Month', 'CreatedDate_Day')")}};hist_CompareToDuration = group hist_CompareToDuration by 'LoyaltyMemberTier_LoyaltyMemberId';hist_CompareToDuration = foreach hist_CompareToDuration generate  'LoyaltyMemberTier_LoyaltyMemberId' as 'LoyaltyMemberId', count() as 'count';result_Duration = union q_Duration, hist_Duration;result_Duration = group result_Duration by 'LoyaltyMemberId';result_Duration = foreach result_Duration  generate 'LoyaltyMemberId' as 'LoyaltyMemberId', unique('LoyaltyMemberId') as 'Count of Members';result_CompareToDuration = union q_CompareToDuration, hist_CompareToDuration;result_CompareToDuration = group result_CompareToDuration by 'LoyaltyMemberId';result_CompareToDuration = foreach result_CompareToDuration  generate 'LoyaltyMemberId' as 'LoyaltyMemberId', unique('LoyaltyMemberId') as 'Count of Members Durations';finalresult = group result_Duration by all full, result_CompareToDuration by all;finalresult = foreach finalresult generate sum(result_Duration.'Count of Members') as 'Count of Members', sum(result_CompareToDuration.'Count of Members Durations') as 'Count of Members Durations',(sum(result_Duration.'Count of Members') - sum(result_CompareToDuration.'Count of Members Durations')*100)/sum(result_CompareToDuration.'Count of Members Durations') as 'Number_of_Members_percentage';

lens_1.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.LoyRcg_SurveyQuestionResponse_with_TransactionJournalRecords53.FullyQualifiedName}";q = filter q by 'SurveyQuestion_QuestionType' == "Rating";Current = filter q by {{row(ActivityDate_2.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Year', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Month','SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Day')")}};Current = foreach Current generate first('NumberValue')/(first('QuestionChoice_MaxValue')) as 'Rating',first('Scale') as 'Scale';Previous = filter q by {{row(ActivityDate_3.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Year', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Month', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Day')")}};Previous = foreach Previous generate  first('NumberValue')/(first('QuestionChoice_MaxValue')) as 'PreviousRating', first('Scale') as 'Scale';result = group Current by all full, Previous by all;result = foreach result generate coalesce(round((sum(Current.'Rating')/count(Current)) * first(Current.'Scale'),2),0) as 'CSAT_Current',coalesce(round((sum(Previous.'PreviousRating')/count(Previous)) * first(Previous.'Scale'),2),0) as 'CSAT_Previous';result = foreach result generate 'CSAT_Current','CSAT_Previous',('CSAT_Current' - 'CSAT_Previous')/'CSAT_Previous' as 'Delta',case when CSAT_Current < 0 then "rgb(232, 67, 64)" else "rgb(58, 232, 103)" end as 'Bar_Color_CSAT';

lens_2.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.LoyRcg_SurveyQuestionResponse_with_TransactionJournalRecords53.FullyQualifiedName}";q = filter q by 'SurveyQuestion_QuestionType' == "Rating";result = foreach q generate (first('NumberValue')/first('QuestionChoice_MaxValue')) * first('Scale') as 'CSATValue', count(q) as 'count';result = group result by all;result = foreach result generate round(sum(CSATValue)/sum(count),2) as 'Program_CSAT';
